{"word":"περιστένω","slug":"περιστένω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>περιστένω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to make narrow, compress</i>: <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>περιστένεται δέ τε γαστήρ</el>, of wolves, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to sound round about</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b>Hhymn.</b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to bemoan</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}